  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinical diagnosis of Irritable Bowel Syndrome according to Rome III criteria

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of inflammatory bowel disease (IBD)

          -  Symptom debut after age of 50

          -  Ongoing severe mental illness (psychosis, severe depression, suicidal ideation,
             bipolar disease)

          -  Inability to participate in internet delivered treatment
      </textblock>
